  "dateStart": "2025-09-02",
  "description": "<p>This single degree program is composed of a selected combination of courses from the <a href=\"#/experiences/rJeiHV5iV\">School of Earth and Ocean Sciences</a> and the <a href=\"#/experiences/r1DAk4co4\">Department of Chemistry</a>. Students complete this program in the <a href=\"#/experiences/rJwWOW5oN\">Faculty of Science</a> and must consult the <a href=\"#/experiences/BylJ9-cs4\">Faculty Program Requirements</a>.</p>",
